Text: Your talk on Monday fwdA minor revision of my earlier email shown below The last line should read I will be waiting in my office from for your call My office phone is Sorry that I have to resend this email Ed Forwarded message Date Thu Feb CST From edward kao disc ayouUHEDU To Vince J Kaminski Subject Your talk on Monday Dear Vince I would like to send out an annoucement about your talk in my Risk Management in the Energy Sector course on February Monday Is it correct that the name of your talk will be Commodity Trading in the Energy Sector You indicated that you would be using transparencies so we have a projector ready for you Please let me know if there is anything else you need for the talk Please also confirm this at your earliest convenience so that I can get announcement sent out soon Thanks in advance for the talk We all look forward to meeting you Monday Best regards Ed PS The class meet pm at Meclcher Hall As we originally planned I will be waiting in my office from and greet you at the parking lot IE
